Rescue Care spokesman Garrith Jamieson said that paramedics were called to the accident scene on the M19 highway near Westville shortly after 6am on Wednesday morning. They found a man, believed to be in his 20s, in the wreckage of the mangled Chevrolet Spark, but he had already succumbed to his injuries and was declared dead at the accident scene. Police were on scene to investigate the accident. African News Agency (ANA)